summary: A complete version of numenume\\\'s bikini.
descriptionHtml:
Compiled Numenume\'s Bikini to a single file.

1. Install CHSBHC - BBP - Nude and Jiggly Mod.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4888
2. Install Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE-.
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

Recommend using bodyslide to create a custom body (see CBBE docs), and enabling CHSBHC-BBP options to avoid CTD for this and other mods that require BBP.
author: Numenume
